Seed Source: Proof that you used non-GMO, untreated seeds.
Inputs: Records of every kilo of manure or "Jeevamrut" (cow urine-based fertilizer) you added.
Buffer Zones: Proof that your neighbor’s chemical spray isn't drifting onto your "Nuskha" crops (usually done by planting a thick hedge of trees).
